_sText:
A quick map I made for Thanksgiving. 

Why did I make this? I was playing CS:S on a bhop server, and someone said there should be a map in which every bhop block had a turkey sound for Thanksgiving. At that moment I was off to create this beauty of a map.  Please rate!

This is a speedrun map and should take under 20 seconds.

Uploaded November 23, 2016.
